        <h1>Capital Gains Tax Rates 2026: Projected Rates and Thresholds</h1>
        <p class="qa-meta">Updated May 2026 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Projected estimates only &nbsp;|&nbsp; Official IRS figures expected October 2026</p>
        <p>The capital gains tax rates for 2026 have not yet been officially announced. The rates of 0%, 15%, and 20% are expected to remain unchanged. Income thresholds for each rate are projected to increase slightly from 2025 levels based on inflation adjustments. This page will be updated when official figures are released.</p>
        <div class="year-nav">
          <a href="/capital-gains-tax-rates-2025">2025 Rates (Official)</a>
          <a href="/capital-gains-tax-rates-2026" class="active">2026 Rates (Projected)</a>
        </div>
      </div>

